data.description: Great location to Fort Carson and Interstate 25.  No stairs.  Nice private patio in back with some growing area for plants, some artificial turf.  Front yard has a nice pear tree.  Access to patio from kitchen or master bedroom.  Fireplace in living room.  HOA maintains dog park in neighborhood.  Refrigerator 3 years old. All windows and 2 sliders replaced in 2019. Kitchen and Bathrooms have new flooring in 2024.
